 /**
  * Integration test for {@link RtReleaseAsset}.
  *
  * @author Carlos Miranda (miranda.cma@gmail.com)
  * @version $Id$
  * @since 0.8
- * @todo #282 Need to implement integration test for RtReleaseAsset. This class
